        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Hiring Incentive to Return Employment Act of 2021 or the HIRE Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill increases the rate of the work opportunity tax credit from 40% to 50% of wages paid to members of the targeted groups eligible for such credit over a two-year period. It also increases to $10,000 the amount of wages taken into account for purposes of the credit.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
